1
00:00:00,570 --> 00:00:02,140
(Yejin Rehabilitation Hospital)

2
00:00:02,140 --> 00:00:03,580
(Episode 85)

3
00:00:24,300 --> 00:00:26,160
Hong Ju, we're saved!

4
00:00:27,170 --> 00:00:29,070
Mom, we're saved!

5
00:00:29,070 --> 00:00:30,240
We're saved!

6
00:00:43,250 --> 00:00:45,880
First, let's go inside and confirm it.

7
00:00:46,280 --> 00:00:47,290
Right.

8
00:00:47,490 --> 00:00:50,860
Mom, why am I so excited? We're saved.

9
00:00:50,860 --> 00:00:52,560
Hey, it's more than just being saved!

10
00:00:52,860 --> 00:00:56,160
Let's find Oh Jang Mi and present her
to the Chairman before anyone else.

11
00:00:56,330 --> 00:00:59,730
What will that wench Chae Hwa Young do?
She'll have to tuck her tail and run.

12
00:00:59,900 --> 00:01:04,070
I'm so thrilled.
I feel like a huge weight has been lifted.

13
00:01:04,470 --> 00:01:06,970
That's right.
The mystery of why CEO Chae had twins...

14
00:01:06,970 --> 00:01:08,870
but only raised one of them...

15
00:01:09,140 --> 00:01:12,110
will be solved once we find Oh Jang Mi
and take her to the Chairman, right?

16
00:01:12,910 --> 00:01:14,480
Let's go.

17
00:01:47,380 --> 00:01:48,410
Did you?

18
00:01:48,410 --> 00:01:50,920
You found the rehabilitation hospital
where Seo Rin is?

19
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:52,280
Yes.

20
00:01:52,780 --> 00:01:54,150
I followed Oh Tae Pyung,

21
00:01:55,020 --> 00:01:56,390
and he led me
to a rehabilitation hospital.

22
00:01:59,690 --> 00:02:01,230
If Oh Tae Pyung went in,

23
00:02:01,230 --> 00:02:03,130
that has to be the hospital
where Seo Rin is.

24
00:02:03,560 --> 00:02:05,960
Manager Lee, so where is it?

25
00:02:07,100 --> 00:02:09,800
Did Manager Lee find Seo Rin's hospital?

26
00:02:10,370 --> 00:02:13,970
Alright. I'm heading there now.
Manager Lee, you handle the rest.

27
00:02:14,340 --> 00:02:16,540
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

28
00:02:26,080 --> 00:02:28,090
- The person you called is unavailable.
- What do I do?

29
00:02:28,090 --> 00:02:30,960
- Connecting to voicemail.
- Come on, please pick up.

30
00:02:32,820 --> 00:02:35,130
Charges will apply after the beep.

31
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:39,560
Tae Pyung, you have to move Seo Rin
out of that hospital now.

32
00:02:39,860 --> 00:02:42,430
Manager Lee found out where she is.
She's in danger.

33
00:02:42,630 --> 00:02:43,740
Call me back.

34
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:46,770
What are you talking about?
Who is in danger?

35
00:02:47,140 --> 00:02:49,640
Chae Hwa Young found out where Seo Rin is.

36
00:02:49,770 --> 00:02:51,240
That is a huge problem.

37
00:02:51,440 --> 00:02:53,180
We must stay one step ahead of CEO Chae.

38
00:02:53,510 --> 00:02:54,550
What about Tae Pyung?

39
00:02:54,610 --> 00:02:56,980
He's not answering his phone.
What should I do?

40
00:02:57,350 --> 00:02:59,220
Let's call him on the way.
We have to hurry.

41
00:02:59,550 --> 00:03:02,390
If CEO Chae finds Seo Rin,
you'll be in danger, Jang Mi.

42
00:03:02,590 --> 00:03:04,560
Then you'll be of no use to her anymore.

43
00:03:04,590 --> 00:03:07,390
We can't let Chae Hwa Young
get her hands on Seo Rin.

44
00:03:07,790 --> 00:03:08,890
Let's go.

45
00:03:10,830 --> 00:03:12,800
Mom, can you see Tok Hee?

46
00:03:13,430 --> 00:03:16,470
- Can you see Seo Rin?
- Yes, I can see her.

47
00:03:16,730 --> 00:03:18,700
I can see our Tok Hee.

48
00:03:21,540 --> 00:03:24,340
- Tok Hee is sick.
- Mom...

49
00:03:24,740 --> 00:03:27,110
Tok Hee will be all better
if she just sleeps a little longer.

50
00:03:27,480 --> 00:03:29,110
Don't you worry. Okay?

51
00:03:29,810 --> 00:03:30,920
Tok Hee...

52
00:03:32,220 --> 00:03:33,750
Please wake up soon.

53
00:03:34,550 --> 00:03:35,950
The doctor said...

54
00:03:36,220 --> 00:03:38,320
that she could wake up one day
just like that.

55
00:03:38,720 --> 00:03:40,890
Please don't worry, Mom. Alright?

56
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:43,260
And no more crying
because you miss Tok Hee, okay?

57
00:03:43,630 --> 00:03:44,700
I'm hanging up now.

58
00:03:52,340 --> 00:03:54,470
Fortunately, the seizure has stopped.

59
00:03:55,440 --> 00:03:56,910
She needs more rest to stabilize.

60
00:04:05,180 --> 00:04:08,320
What? The name is Kim Chun Sik.
Is this the wrong room?

61
00:04:08,390 --> 00:04:11,460
This can't be it.
The patient is 75 years old.

62
00:04:11,590 --> 00:04:13,830
- We were barking up the wrong tree.
- You're right.

63
00:04:25,170 --> 00:04:26,900
I'll be on my way now.

64
00:04:27,540 --> 00:04:28,540
Please take good care of her.

65
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:30,040
Take care.

66
00:04:40,390 --> 00:04:41,390
Excuse me!

67
00:04:42,990 --> 00:04:44,360
Who are you here to visit?

68
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:47,360
We're here to see Mr. Kim Chun Sik.

69
00:04:47,460 --> 00:04:49,760
What's your relationship
to the patient in this room?

70
00:04:51,200 --> 00:04:52,360
We're...

71
00:04:54,430 --> 00:04:56,670
We're distant relatives
of Mr. Kim Chun Sik.

72
00:04:58,040 --> 00:05:01,110
This patient needs complete rest,
so no visitors are allowed.

73
00:05:01,310 --> 00:05:04,340
What? That's ridiculous!
If I want to see him, I'll see him.

74
00:05:04,410 --> 00:05:05,740
- Move, get out of the way!
- Move!

75
00:05:05,810 --> 00:05:06,880
I can't let you in there.

76
00:05:06,880 --> 00:05:08,810
If you make a scene, I'll call security.

77
00:05:09,580 --> 00:05:11,150
Go ahead, call them!

78
00:05:11,220 --> 00:05:12,780
I dare you! Now, get out of my way!

79
00:05:12,780 --> 00:05:14,950
The patient's guardian said
no visitors were allowed.

80
00:05:14,950 --> 00:05:17,520
If you wish to visit,
you need the guardian's permission first.

81
00:05:17,590 --> 00:05:19,760
- Seriously...
- Excuse me! You two!

82
00:05:22,830 --> 00:05:23,930
Get out.

83
00:05:24,530 --> 00:05:26,760
Keep it up, I'll call the cops. Got it?

84
00:05:26,760 --> 00:05:29,100
- No, wait. We're here to...
- Get out.

85
00:05:29,100 --> 00:05:30,570
I said, get out!

86
00:05:30,700 --> 00:05:31,970
I said, go!

87
00:05:31,970 --> 00:05:33,870
- Just go! Please, leave.
- Oh my goodness!

88
00:05:38,540 --> 00:05:39,710
Is everything ready?

89
00:05:40,140 --> 00:05:42,710
(Korea University Hospital)

90
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:01,230
Honey.

91
00:06:01,730 --> 00:06:03,200
What are we going to do about Jun Ho?

92
00:06:03,900 --> 00:06:06,500
He's in so much pain,
but he won't even cry out.

93
00:06:07,410 --> 00:06:10,610
Jun Ho, it's okay to cry out if it hurts.

94
00:06:11,180 --> 00:06:12,480
I'm feeling a little better now.

95
00:06:12,840 --> 00:06:14,750
You must be in so much pain.

96
00:06:14,950 --> 00:06:17,480
He has a very high pain tolerance.

97
00:06:17,750 --> 00:06:20,150
When will he be able to go home?

98
00:06:21,020 --> 00:06:22,120
Honey.

99
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:24,360
He must stay until he's fully recovered.

100
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:25,860
You can't think
of taking him home already.

101
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:27,890
The doctor will have the final say,

102
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:30,260
but he can switch to outpatient care now.

103
00:06:31,130 --> 00:06:32,160
That's a relief.

104
00:06:33,530 --> 00:06:34,870
I'm just getting sick of being here, Mom.

105
00:06:35,300 --> 00:06:37,070
Yes, I can imagine.

106
00:06:37,440 --> 00:06:39,470
I thought the woman
who visits him every day...

107
00:06:40,240 --> 00:06:41,940
was his mother.

108
00:06:42,440 --> 00:06:45,640
She cares for him so deeply.

109
00:06:47,280 --> 00:06:48,350
Excuse me?

110
00:06:48,780 --> 00:06:49,850
Who?

111
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:51,650
CEO Chae.

112
00:06:52,520 --> 00:06:54,350
That was really kind of her.

113
00:06:55,020 --> 00:06:58,590
She must feel incredibly guilty
since it happened at the company.

114
00:06:58,860 --> 00:07:01,460
Plus, he got hurt saving her daughter.

115
00:07:01,960 --> 00:07:03,290
Of course she'd feel responsible.

116
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:08,430
Still, I'm seeing CEO Chae in a new light,
taking care of our Jun Ho like that.

117
00:07:14,870 --> 00:07:18,280
(Yejin Rehabilitation Hospital)

118
00:07:19,210 --> 00:07:20,340
Looks like a fire.

119
00:07:20,410 --> 00:07:22,880
- Hey, this way!
- Wait! The patients come first!

120
00:07:22,950 --> 00:07:24,150
Come on, hurry!

121
00:07:36,830 --> 00:07:38,860
Hurry and move her.
We don't have much time.

122
00:07:38,860 --> 00:07:39,930
- Yes, sir.
- Yes, sir.

123
00:07:46,540 --> 00:07:49,110
Tae Pyung, you have to move Seo Rin
out of that hospital now.

124
00:07:49,510 --> 00:07:52,210
Manager Lee found out where Seo Rin is.
We're in danger.

125
00:07:55,710 --> 00:07:57,820
(Under the Anti-Graft Act,
we cannot accept any gifts.)

126
00:08:33,520 --> 00:08:34,550
(Comprehensive Nursing Care Service)

127
00:08:37,990 --> 00:08:42,060
Who would leave this on in the hall?
I seriously thought there was a fire.

128
00:08:42,130 --> 00:08:43,390
Tell me about it.

129
00:08:43,860 --> 00:08:47,060
Still, I'm glad the power came back on
so quickly.

130
00:08:47,300 --> 00:08:48,700
Excuse me, nurse! Seo Rin...

131
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:51,500
- Jang Mi is gone!
- Oh my!

132
00:08:52,300 --> 00:08:53,300
What do we do?

133
00:08:53,770 --> 00:08:55,510
She's the patient who had a seizure
early this morning.

134
00:08:55,740 --> 00:08:58,380
Don't tell me someone took her
during the blackout.

135
00:08:58,740 --> 00:08:59,940
Those bastards.

136
00:09:11,920 --> 00:09:12,920
The wheelchair...

137
00:09:22,800 --> 00:09:23,800
Hurry!

138
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:32,080
Manager Lee!

139
00:09:32,980 --> 00:09:33,980
Manager Lee!

140
00:09:36,280 --> 00:09:37,280
Stop right there!

141
00:09:48,090 --> 00:09:51,630
- Jang Mi, how close are you?
- I'm almost there.

142
00:09:52,260 --> 00:09:53,360
I was a step too late.

143
00:09:53,660 --> 00:09:55,930
What do I do? They got Seo Rin!

144
00:09:55,930 --> 00:09:57,600
What? They got her?

145
00:09:57,900 --> 00:09:59,240
What are we going to do, Tae Pyung?

146
00:10:15,450 --> 00:10:17,120
Manager Lee, move it!

147
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:18,990
Ma'am, Oh Tae Pyung is right behind us.

148
00:10:19,260 --> 00:10:21,530
- We have to go now.
- Then hurry!

149
00:10:21,990 --> 00:10:24,000
Before that little wench,
Oh Jang Mi, gets here.

150
00:10:25,330 --> 00:10:27,230
Hurry! Come on, hurry up!

151
00:10:27,700 --> 00:10:29,130
What are you dawdling for?

152
00:10:30,230 --> 00:10:31,240
Get her in!

153
00:10:34,510 --> 00:10:35,510
Close the doors!

154
00:10:52,460 --> 00:10:53,460
Tae Pyung!

155
00:11:14,910 --> 00:11:17,080
Seo Rin, it's me. It's your mother.

156
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:19,780
Seo Rin, please, wake up.

157
00:11:19,780 --> 00:11:20,820
Seo Rin?

158
00:11:23,590 --> 00:11:25,060
Oh Jang Mi, you despicable witch!

159
00:11:25,990 --> 00:11:30,260
Seo Rin, whom I raised for 30 years,
ended up like this all because of you.

160
00:11:30,530 --> 00:11:31,800
This is all your fault!

161
00:11:33,030 --> 00:11:36,070
This should have been you,
not my daughter.

162
00:11:37,970 --> 00:11:40,600
Oh Jang Mi, you think I'll let you live?

163
00:11:41,210 --> 00:11:42,870
I'll make you pay for this.

164
00:11:51,180 --> 00:11:52,220
I'm sorry.

165
00:11:53,280 --> 00:11:55,620
When I got the call at dawn
that Seo Rin was having a seizure,

166
00:11:56,390 --> 00:11:57,820
I just took off without thinking.

167
00:11:58,160 --> 00:12:00,830
No, it's okay.
I would've done the same thing.

168
00:12:00,930 --> 00:12:03,130
She's right, Tae Pyung.
Don't be too hard on yourself.

169
00:12:03,490 --> 00:12:05,330
Come on, let's focus on
finding Seo Rin instead.

170
00:12:06,300 --> 00:12:09,370
Now that CEO Chae has found Seo Rin,

171
00:12:09,730 --> 00:12:10,970
Jang Mi is the one in danger now.

172
00:12:12,700 --> 00:12:15,540
- Don't worry about me.
- How can I not worry?

173
00:12:15,840 --> 00:12:17,980
She's tried to hurt you
so many times before.

174
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:23,480
And now that she's found Seo Rin,
she'll want to make you pay for it all.

175
00:12:24,480 --> 00:12:26,250
What? Goodness.

176
00:12:27,620 --> 00:12:30,220
It's Jang Mi! Jang Mi's here!

177
00:12:32,020 --> 00:12:33,520
Mom.

178
00:12:33,560 --> 00:12:35,830
Have you been well, Mom?

179
00:12:36,030 --> 00:12:37,760
I'm so happy to see you.

180
00:12:38,560 --> 00:12:40,230
I'm going to see Ok Hee and Tok Hee.

181
00:12:40,230 --> 00:12:42,870
Suk Hee is going to see Tok Hee.

182
00:12:43,070 --> 00:12:46,070
Mom, you just video chatted
with Tok Hee a little while ago.

183
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:51,680
Tok Hee is sleeping.
I don't want to say goodbye to Jang Mi.

184
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:53,440
Ok Hee, Tok Hee, okay?

185
00:12:53,510 --> 00:12:55,410
Ok Hee and Tok Hee.

186
00:12:55,410 --> 00:12:56,810
I wonder why the Chairman is calling.

187
00:12:58,020 --> 00:12:59,020
You should answer that.

188
00:13:01,850 --> 00:13:02,850
Yes, Chairman.

189
00:13:04,420 --> 00:13:05,460
Right now?

190
00:13:06,820 --> 00:13:08,690
Yes, I understand. I'll be right there.

191
00:13:13,930 --> 00:13:15,970
You were a huge help today, Manager Lee.

192
00:13:17,400 --> 00:13:19,800
I never would have found Seo Rin
without you.

193
00:13:20,940 --> 00:13:21,940
Thank you.

194
00:13:24,070 --> 00:13:26,210
I finally found my Seo Rin.

195
00:13:26,910 --> 00:13:28,880
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

196
00:13:29,610 --> 00:13:32,050
Now that Oh Jang Mi
has served her purpose,

197
00:13:32,050 --> 00:13:33,180
what should I do with her?

198
00:13:33,980 --> 00:13:37,250
To think she managed to survive this long
just by pretending to be Seo Rin.

199
00:13:38,320 --> 00:13:39,390
Oh Jang Mi.

200
00:13:40,390 --> 00:13:42,430
Your days are numbered.

201
00:13:42,990 --> 00:13:44,060
You filthy witch!

202
00:13:44,660 --> 00:13:47,600
Right.
Yeom San Wol and Jin Hong Ju also know.

203
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:48,630
What?

204
00:13:48,700 --> 00:13:51,700
The nurses stopped them from entering,
so don't worry.

205
00:13:52,270 --> 00:13:56,570
Fine. Let's just sit back and watch
how those two lowlifes react.

206
00:13:57,440 --> 00:13:59,980
Let's see if they're still faithfully
following my orders.

207
00:14:06,050 --> 00:14:09,550
Now that we know where Oh Jang Mi is,
half the battle is won.

208
00:14:09,920 --> 00:14:13,060
We just have to pick the right moment
to drag Oh Jang Mi to the Chairman.

209
00:14:14,460 --> 00:14:15,460
I like the sound of that.

210
00:14:21,070 --> 00:14:22,100
Mrs. Yang!

211
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:27,940
- Yes? What is it?
- Where did the Chairman go?

212
00:14:28,470 --> 00:14:30,310
Why is the house so quiet?

213
00:14:30,610 --> 00:14:33,410
Lawyer Kang Baek Ho came here,
and they left together.

214
00:14:33,880 --> 00:14:36,980
You're saying my Baek Ho was here?
What for?

215
00:14:40,180 --> 00:14:42,320
- You're here?
- How are you feeling?

216
00:14:43,920 --> 00:14:45,490
I'm not here as your little brother today.

217
00:14:45,920 --> 00:14:47,930
I'm here as Kang Baek Ho,
a lawyer for the Dream Group.

218
00:14:49,030 --> 00:14:50,030
What?

219
00:14:53,900 --> 00:14:55,400
Chairman. What brings you here?

220
00:14:55,470 --> 00:14:57,300
It's all right. Stay comfortable.

221
00:14:57,670 --> 00:14:59,870
You don't have to get up.
Please, stay seated.

222
00:15:01,510 --> 00:15:02,510
Lawyer Kang.

223
00:15:02,910 --> 00:15:03,910
Yes.

224
00:15:04,280 --> 00:15:07,410
As per the Chairman's directive,
two percent of Dream Hotel shares...

225
00:15:07,710 --> 00:15:09,850
are to be transferred to you,
General Manager Kang Jun Ho.

226
00:15:16,050 --> 00:15:18,820
- Wait, what is all this?
- It's a little something I prepared.

227
00:15:20,820 --> 00:15:23,160
A token of my gratitude
for saving Seo Rin.

228
00:15:23,730 --> 00:15:25,900
A simple "thank you" isn't enough, is it?

229
00:15:26,300 --> 00:15:28,930
Not after you saved my granddaughter,
who is more precious than my life.

230
00:15:30,100 --> 00:15:32,270
- Sir...
- As a reward for saving my granddaughter,

231
00:15:32,270 --> 00:15:34,670
I'd like to give you a stake in our hotel.

232
00:15:34,810 --> 00:15:35,970
Please accept it.

233
00:15:35,970 --> 00:15:39,480
Think of it as my request to continue
protecting my granddaughter.

234
00:15:39,740 --> 00:15:41,080
It's not a handout, so just accept it.

235
00:15:45,150 --> 00:15:46,150
I can't accept this, sir.

236
00:15:49,350 --> 00:15:50,350
You can't?

237
00:15:50,950 --> 00:15:53,160
Why? Is it not enough?

238
00:15:54,660 --> 00:15:57,730
As far as I'm concerned,
this is as generous as it gets.

239
00:15:58,760 --> 00:16:01,430
I didn't save Seo Rin
expecting anything in return.

240
00:16:02,530 --> 00:16:06,440
I only did what had to be done.
I was just acting on instinct.

241
00:16:07,100 --> 00:16:09,510
The instinct to protect the woman I love.

242
00:16:10,310 --> 00:16:11,310
Love?

243
00:16:11,780 --> 00:16:12,780
Any man...

244
00:16:13,080 --> 00:16:16,650
would've done the same
for the woman he loves.

245
00:16:18,050 --> 00:16:19,320
And you're offering me shares for that?

246
00:16:19,950 --> 00:16:21,720
I must refuse. It's just not appropriate.

247
00:16:22,250 --> 00:16:23,250
I'm sorry.

248
00:16:34,230 --> 00:16:37,770
All right. We'll forget this discussion
about the shares ever happened.

249
00:16:38,400 --> 00:16:39,600
Is that all right with you?

250
00:16:40,170 --> 00:16:42,240
Yes. That's all I ask.

251
00:16:42,770 --> 00:16:45,040
I love Seo Rin unconditionally.

252
00:16:45,510 --> 00:16:47,240
Alright, I understand.

253
00:16:47,510 --> 00:16:49,280
Well, then, just focus on your recovery.

254
00:16:50,150 --> 00:16:51,280
All right, let's go.

255
00:17:06,260 --> 00:17:07,260
Shin Ae Ran.

256
00:17:07,660 --> 00:17:10,670
If you're hiding because of Ssangkal,
I can help you.

257
00:17:10,870 --> 00:17:11,870
Call me.

258
00:17:18,940 --> 00:17:21,380
Goodness. What are you doing here?

259
00:17:21,580 --> 00:17:26,020
Shouldn't you be nursing Prince Charming,
who risked his life to save you?

260
00:17:27,480 --> 00:17:29,490
Aren't you too old for "Prince Charming"?

261
00:17:29,620 --> 00:17:31,090
Snap out of it, Jin Hong Ju.

262
00:17:31,160 --> 00:17:34,590
I heard even the Chairman went
to thank General Manager Kang...

263
00:17:34,590 --> 00:17:35,930
for saving you.

264
00:17:36,160 --> 00:17:37,260
Grandfather did?

265
00:17:42,930 --> 00:17:44,200
Kang Jun Ho.

266
00:17:45,100 --> 00:17:47,700
He gave me the exact answer
I was looking for.

267
00:17:49,210 --> 00:17:50,370
He passed my test.

268
00:17:51,210 --> 00:17:52,210
Yes, sir.

269
00:17:52,810 --> 00:17:57,580
If Seo Rin agrees,
I think I'll have her marry Kang Jun Ho.

270
00:17:59,050 --> 00:18:03,020
All I've ever wanted is someone
who genuinely loves our Seo Rin,

271
00:18:03,490 --> 00:18:05,060
and he had that very look in his eyes.

272
00:18:07,420 --> 00:18:10,030
To think he'd save Seo Rin
without any regard for his own life.

273
00:18:10,330 --> 00:18:13,200
On top of that,
he turned down such a generous offer.

274
00:18:14,360 --> 00:18:15,770
That kid...

275
00:18:15,970 --> 00:18:17,630
He's no ordinary man.

276
00:18:17,970 --> 00:18:20,070
He's highly regarded for his work
at the hotel.

277
00:18:20,400 --> 00:18:21,540
His track record is excellent, too.

278
00:18:22,240 --> 00:18:24,740
It seems CEO Chae's judgment
about him was spot on.

279
00:18:24,880 --> 00:18:26,310
Indeed.

280
00:18:26,480 --> 00:18:30,180
Marrying Seo Rin off
to General Manager Kang...

281
00:18:31,110 --> 00:18:33,350
- sounds like a good idea.
- Oh my.

282
00:18:34,750 --> 00:18:38,520
Honey, will you really make Seo Rin
marry Kang Jun Ho?

283
00:18:38,860 --> 00:18:40,960
Only if Seo Rin agrees, of course.

284
00:18:51,270 --> 00:18:52,700
Jun Ho, what do you think you're doing?

285
00:18:52,970 --> 00:18:54,840
I just ran into the doctor,

286
00:18:54,910 --> 00:18:57,640
and he said you were checking yourself out
to get outpatient treatment?

287
00:18:57,840 --> 00:19:00,040
In your condition?
Are you out of your mind?

288
00:19:00,480 --> 00:19:04,050
If your wound gets infected,
it'll leave a nasty scar!

289
00:19:04,110 --> 00:19:05,280
I'll be fine.

290
00:19:06,020 --> 00:19:07,250
I can't stand being cooped up
in a hospital.

291
00:19:07,720 --> 00:19:10,220
I know you have bad memories of hospitals.

292
00:19:11,020 --> 00:19:14,760
But right now, just listen to me
and stay here for your treatment.

293
00:19:15,660 --> 00:19:16,990
I told you I was fine.

294
00:19:17,630 --> 00:19:18,960
I can take care of myself.

295
00:19:19,630 --> 00:19:20,660
You're so stubborn.

296
00:19:22,830 --> 00:19:23,930
The Chairman was here.

297
00:19:24,200 --> 00:19:25,200
What?

298
00:19:25,800 --> 00:19:28,910
Don't tell me he thanked you
for saving Seo Rin...

299
00:19:29,410 --> 00:19:30,940
and gave you his blessing to marry.

300
00:19:30,940 --> 00:19:33,180
I turned down his offer of shares.

301
00:19:34,880 --> 00:19:37,980
The Chairman might let Seo Rin and I
get married.

302
00:19:38,880 --> 00:19:41,720
So I need you to move forward
with that in mind.

303
00:19:42,650 --> 00:19:43,850
I need you to speed things up.

304
00:19:44,050 --> 00:19:46,620
No, that won't be necessary anymore.

305
00:19:47,120 --> 00:19:48,430
What do you mean, it won't be necessary?

306
00:19:51,530 --> 00:19:53,930
You're the man
who saved his one and only granddaughter.

307
00:19:54,260 --> 00:19:55,970
Of course he'd come to pay his respects.

308
00:19:56,970 --> 00:19:58,140
Gosh, Mom.

309
00:19:58,140 --> 00:20:00,940
You're practically camping out
in General Manager Kang's room.

310
00:20:01,470 --> 00:20:03,840
What's with all the secrecy?

311
00:20:04,140 --> 00:20:05,440
I'm glad you're here, Seo Rin.

312
00:20:06,310 --> 00:20:08,450
It was General Manager Kang who got hurt
and not you.

313
00:20:09,010 --> 00:20:12,080
He saved your life.
You should stay by his side.

314
00:20:12,650 --> 00:20:14,020
It's the decent thing to do.

315
00:20:15,420 --> 00:20:17,320
- Decency?
- Seo Rin.

316
00:20:18,220 --> 00:20:20,420
I feel so cooped up.
Could you take me out for a walk?

317
00:20:27,900 --> 00:20:29,730
All set? Let's get going.

318
00:20:29,730 --> 00:20:31,030
Yes, I'm ready.

319
00:20:36,440 --> 00:20:38,740
- It's CEO Chae.
- She's calling you?

320
00:20:39,280 --> 00:20:41,580
- Answer it, quick.
- Okay.

321
00:20:44,250 --> 00:20:45,780
Yes, this is Jun Ho's mother.

322
00:20:45,920 --> 00:20:47,950
Why wasn't there a guardian
with him in his room?

323
00:20:49,220 --> 00:20:50,420
The thing is,

324
00:20:50,420 --> 00:20:53,860
Jun Ho was craving some soup,
so I just stepped out for a moment.

325
00:20:54,890 --> 00:20:57,360
Is something wrong?
Did something happen to Jun Ho?

326
00:20:57,530 --> 00:20:59,560
General Manager Kang is trying
to get discharged from the hospital now.

327
00:20:59,900 --> 00:21:01,730
It's not like he has no family.

328
00:21:02,100 --> 00:21:04,230
How could you let him make that decision
on his own?

329
00:21:04,330 --> 00:21:06,200
He wants to leave the hospital?

330
00:21:07,000 --> 00:21:08,270
Jun Ho wants to be discharged?

331
00:21:08,570 --> 00:21:11,010
Fortunately,
I was able to stop him from leaving.

332
00:21:12,080 --> 00:21:15,180
He said he felt cooped up,
so he's out for a walk with Seo Rin.

333
00:21:16,810 --> 00:21:17,910
That's a relief.

334
00:21:18,020 --> 00:21:20,180
He must hate hospitals
after all the time he spent there...

335
00:21:20,180 --> 00:21:21,790
for his leukemia treatments.

336
00:21:21,920 --> 00:21:25,590
I believe a patient needs a guardian
with them at all times.

337
00:21:26,260 --> 00:21:27,860
I'm hanging up now.

338
00:21:30,030 --> 00:21:32,400
Is it because he's not her biological son?

339
00:21:33,830 --> 00:21:37,370
Anyway, it's moments like these
that show she's just the stepmother.

340
00:21:40,140 --> 00:21:43,170
Oh Jang Mi must be frantically
looking for Seo Rin.

341
00:21:44,270 --> 00:21:47,410
The real Seo Rin needs to wake up soon
so I can figure out what to do with her.

342
00:21:57,190 --> 00:21:58,190
Here you go.

343
00:22:02,630 --> 00:22:04,530
Are patients allowed to drink coffee?

344
00:22:05,460 --> 00:22:08,100
It's just my arm.
It's not like I have an internal injury.

345
00:22:13,100 --> 00:22:14,840
I've missed drinking coffee.

346
00:22:17,070 --> 00:22:18,140
And I've missed you.

347
00:22:19,210 --> 00:22:21,140
- Excuse me?
- You didn't hear me?

348
00:22:21,850 --> 00:22:23,110
I said I've missed you.

349
00:22:25,320 --> 00:22:26,820
I'm grateful you saved me,

350
00:22:27,080 --> 00:22:28,320
but I'm going to pretend
I didn't hear that.

351
00:22:31,920 --> 00:22:32,920
When I was a kid,

352
00:22:33,860 --> 00:22:36,030
I spent more time in the hospital
than I did at home.

353
00:22:37,460 --> 00:22:39,200
That's why I can't even stand
the sight of a hospital.

354
00:22:41,900 --> 00:22:43,070
Things that other people...

355
00:22:43,370 --> 00:22:46,470
take for granted,
like a normal family and a normal life,

356
00:22:47,840 --> 00:22:50,310
I had to fight
with everything I had to get.

357
00:22:51,110 --> 00:22:53,840
I heard you had leukemia.

358
00:22:54,850 --> 00:22:56,350
Are you talking about your health?

359
00:22:58,380 --> 00:23:00,680
Nothing in my life has ever come easy.

360
00:23:01,720 --> 00:23:02,750
Not my health...

361
00:23:03,790 --> 00:23:04,890
nor my family.

362
00:23:11,560 --> 00:23:14,560
I thought you took Chairman Ma home.
What are you still doing here?

363
00:23:14,730 --> 00:23:16,130
I have something to discuss with Seo Rin.

364
00:23:16,830 --> 00:23:18,440
Director Ma, could I have a word with you?

365
00:23:18,870 --> 00:23:19,870
Sure.

366
00:23:28,040 --> 00:23:29,050
Don't go.

367
00:23:34,220 --> 00:23:35,450
If you have something to say, say it here.

368
00:23:36,690 --> 00:23:37,920
Kang Baek Ho, didn't I tell you?

369
00:23:38,790 --> 00:23:40,060
Stay away from Seo Rin.

370
00:23:41,360 --> 00:23:43,630
I'm a lawyer on this company's legal team.

371
00:23:44,530 --> 00:23:45,930
And Ma Seo Rin
is the Chairman's granddaughter.

372
00:23:46,760 --> 00:23:49,170
Do I really need to explain
the legal implications in front of you?

373
00:23:49,530 --> 00:23:50,870
Why do you have to do that right now?

374
00:23:51,370 --> 00:23:54,070
You're just making an excuse.
You think I can't see that?

375
00:23:54,840 --> 00:23:57,370
You're only doing this because
you don't want me alone with Seo Rin.

376
00:23:57,540 --> 00:24:00,080
- I just needed to talk to her.
- Baek Ho.

377
00:24:00,840 --> 00:24:02,910
Didn't I tell you she was
going to be your sister-in-law?

378
00:24:03,610 --> 00:24:05,620
I said you needed to stay away from her.

379
00:24:06,120 --> 00:24:07,750
- But every single time...
- Stop it.

380
00:24:08,320 --> 00:24:09,750
Both of you, just stop.

381
00:24:09,950 --> 00:24:11,350
What am I, some kind of object?

382
00:24:11,820 --> 00:24:14,190
I get to decide who I like.

383
00:24:14,890 --> 00:24:16,460
You're acting as if I'm not even here.

384
00:24:16,960 --> 00:24:18,860
Why are you two trying to dictate
my feelings?

385
00:24:19,600 --> 00:24:23,330
Whether I like Baek Ho or dislike Jun Ho,
those are my feelings to have.

386
00:24:23,470 --> 00:24:24,470
Got it?

387
00:24:25,200 --> 00:24:26,200
So don't you ever...

388
00:24:26,470 --> 00:24:28,710
argue about my feelings
in front of me again.

389
00:24:29,140 --> 00:24:30,140
It's insulting.

390
00:24:46,060 --> 00:24:48,560
How is General Manager Kang?

391
00:24:48,560 --> 00:24:50,460
Is he feeling any better?

392
00:24:51,190 --> 00:24:52,200
Yes.

393
00:24:52,530 --> 00:24:55,530
He still needs more treatment
for his injuries to fully heal,

394
00:24:55,930 --> 00:24:59,270
but General Manager Kang is very eager
to get back to the office.

395
00:24:59,670 --> 00:25:01,140
I've been trying to talk him out of it.

396
00:25:02,510 --> 00:25:04,040
He's a responsible man.

397
00:25:04,810 --> 00:25:08,450
Even after he's discharged,
tell him he can take more time off...

398
00:25:08,680 --> 00:25:11,050
so he doesn't have any setbacks.

399
00:25:12,680 --> 00:25:13,780
Thank you, Father.

400
00:25:15,150 --> 00:25:16,490
What are you thanking him for?

401
00:25:16,620 --> 00:25:18,020
Are you two a thing or something?

402
00:25:18,960 --> 00:25:20,290
But knowing General Manager Kang,

403
00:25:20,560 --> 00:25:24,730
he'll be out in a day or two
and come right back to work.

404
00:25:24,830 --> 00:25:26,660
Well, General Manager Kang
needs to come back soon anyway...

405
00:25:26,660 --> 00:25:29,000
to clean up the mess you made, Mom,
doesn't he?

406
00:25:29,270 --> 00:25:30,270
Ma Seo Rin.

407
00:25:30,900 --> 00:25:32,370
Have you forgotten I was found innocent?

408
00:25:32,970 --> 00:25:34,240
What mess is there to clean up?

409
00:25:34,570 --> 00:25:36,210
The stock price has already recovered.

410
00:25:36,210 --> 00:25:38,040
Well, the stock price's recovery...

411
00:25:38,210 --> 00:25:41,780
is only because my darling husband
took care of everything.

412
00:25:43,010 --> 00:25:44,280
Isn't that right, dear?

413
00:25:45,250 --> 00:25:46,250
CEO Chae.

414
00:25:46,750 --> 00:25:47,780
Have Seo Rin...

415
00:25:48,420 --> 00:25:50,820
prepare for her wedding to Kang Jun Ho.

416
00:25:50,820 --> 00:25:52,890
- Father.
- Grandfather.

417
00:25:53,720 --> 00:25:54,890
I refuse.

418
00:25:55,160 --> 00:25:57,690
Don't tell me this is because
Kang Jun Ho saved me.

419
00:25:58,360 --> 00:26:00,960
What did General Manager Kang tell you,
Grandfather?

420
00:26:02,170 --> 00:26:04,470
Seo Rin, do you think I don't know
how fickle you can be?

421
00:26:04,800 --> 00:26:06,600
You change your mind a dozen times a day.

422
00:26:08,540 --> 00:26:11,610
I can see that
Jun Ho is truly sincere about you.

423
00:26:12,040 --> 00:26:13,040
Don't you see?

424
00:26:20,920 --> 00:26:21,990
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

425
00:26:22,050 --> 00:26:24,690
Chairman Ma gave his blessing
for Jun Ho and Seo Rin's marriage.

426
00:26:26,160 --> 00:26:29,190
So you're planning to go ahead
with the wedding?

427
00:26:29,830 --> 00:26:32,430
It's too soon to get rid of Oh Jang Mi...

428
00:26:33,030 --> 00:26:34,860
while Seo Rin is still unconscious.

429
00:26:35,700 --> 00:26:37,370
First, we get them married.

430
00:26:38,000 --> 00:26:40,100
Once Jun Ho is at the point of no return,

431
00:26:40,800 --> 00:26:42,570
we'll get rid of Oh Jang Mi...

432
00:26:42,910 --> 00:26:45,110
and swap her out for Seo Rin.
We have no other choice.

433
00:26:45,610 --> 00:26:47,680
What if the real Seo Rin
doesn't wake up by then?

434
00:26:49,650 --> 00:26:52,680
We'll have to stage an accident
that puts her in a coma.

435
00:26:53,820 --> 00:26:56,520
Securing Dream Hotel through this marriage
is the priority.

436
00:26:57,120 --> 00:27:00,420
If it comes to that, even Chairman Ma
will have no choice but to fall for it.

437
00:27:01,320 --> 00:27:02,690
We need to rush the wedding.

438
00:27:04,860 --> 00:27:08,260
Hey, Tae Pyung.
I think I've found a way to find Seo Rin.

439
00:27:08,530 --> 00:27:09,930
What? How?

440
00:27:09,930 --> 00:27:11,570
I checked my dashcam,

441
00:27:12,000 --> 00:27:14,700
and a private ambulance was leaving
just as I was pulling in.

442
00:27:20,780 --> 00:27:22,880
I'm sure Seo Rin was in that ambulance.

443
00:27:23,150 --> 00:27:24,710
Luckily, the dashcam caught
the license plate.

444
00:27:25,020 --> 00:27:26,220
That's a huge break.

445
00:27:26,220 --> 00:27:28,120
We have to find Seo Rin, no matter what.

446
00:27:28,550 --> 00:27:31,250
If Chae Hwa Young has Seo Rin,
everyone is in danger.

447
00:27:31,860 --> 00:27:32,860
Especially Jang Mi.

448
00:27:37,860 --> 00:27:38,960
Welcome, my dear daughter.

449
00:27:40,900 --> 00:27:43,570
So you're finally getting married
to Kang Jun Ho.

450
00:27:44,170 --> 00:27:45,170
Oh Jang Mi.

451
00:27:45,870 --> 00:27:47,400
Who says I'm getting married?

452
00:27:47,940 --> 00:27:50,310
Chae Hwa Young,
do you really think you'll get your way?

453
00:28:20,600 --> 00:28:22,040
(The First Man)

454
00:28:22,110 --> 00:28:24,040
Hey, don't do this! Stop it!

455
00:28:24,070 --> 00:28:26,180
Chae Hwa Young, what have you done now?

456
00:28:26,180 --> 00:28:28,010
You shameless monster!

457
00:28:28,340 --> 00:28:29,480
This is CEO Chae's spoon.

458
00:28:29,910 --> 00:28:32,920
If we can prove that Chae Hwa Young
is Kang Jun Ho's mother,

459
00:28:33,380 --> 00:28:35,250
I'm going to show
that evidence to Grandfather.

460
00:28:35,790 --> 00:28:38,620
What if Jang Mi really ends up
marrying your brother?

461
00:28:39,320 --> 00:28:41,490
I'm going to marry you, Seo Rin.

462
00:28:41,490 --> 00:28:42,630
I'm...

463
00:28:42,930 --> 00:28:44,190
not Ma Seo Rin.

464
00:28:44,790 --> 00:28:45,800
I'm Oh Jang Mi.

465
00:28:51,940 --> 00:28:53,940
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
